Reasoning: The paper proposes a method for joint learning of concepts and metaconcepts from images and associated question-answer pairs. This involves visual recognition and understanding, as well as natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves some aspects of natural language processing (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE).
